{"blogid": "124893183", "writerAge": "码龄1年", "writerBlogNum": "22", "writerCollect": "250", "writerComment": "74", "writerFan": "3609", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "481", "writerName": "玄予", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_124893183.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "30700", "writerRankWeekly": "1379", "writerThumb": "101", "writerVisitNum": "340988", "blog_read_count": "14164", "blog_time": "已于 2022-08-13 16:06:11 修改", "blog_title": "[已解决] wordpress：您的PHP似乎没有安装运行WordPress所必需的MySQL扩展", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p>今天安装<a href=\"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=wordpress&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020\" title=\"wordpress\">wordpress</a>，按照教程搭好了lamp环境，主机访问IP地址后提示：<em><strong>您的PHP似乎没有安装</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>运行WordPress所必需的MySQL扩展</strong></em>，在网上找了解决办法全是一些复制粘贴的离谱的办法。</p>\n<p>这里一般分两种情况</p>\n<h3>1：php版本问题</h3>\n<p>wordpress官方推荐php版本是7.4以上</p>\n<p>查看php版本</p>\n<pre><code>php -v\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"134\" src=\"image\\8295759c13184ff3939517f9e291801c.png\" width=\"780\"/></p>\n<p>这样就可以查看php版本了</p>\n<p>如果低于7.4请更换php版本</p>\n<p>这个网上有很多教程，这里就不多阐述了</p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#fe2c24;\">完成后记得重启电脑</span></p>\n<h3>2：php的php-mysql扩展</h3>\n<p><strong>1:ubuntu</strong></p>\n<p>安装php-mysql</p>\n<pre><code>sudo apt install php-mysql</code></pre>\n<p><strong>2:centos</strong></p>\n<p>安装php-mysqlnd</p>\n<pre><code>yum install php-mysqlnd</code></pre>\n<p>重启电脑</p>\n<p>至此问题解决</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>如果还疑问的话也欢迎在下方告诉我</p>\n</div>\n</div>"}